object.customQuery:
select * from dbo.Job_Completion_GW_And_PMS where id=(select max(id) from dbo.Job_Completion_GW_And_PMS)

UNION ALL
SELECT 
    CASE 
        WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN 1
        ELSE NULL
    END AS Id,
    CASE 
        WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN 'Y'
        ELSE NULL
    END AS GW_Completion_Flg,
   CASE 
        WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN 'Y'
        ELSE NULL
    END AS PMS_Completion_Flg,
   CASE 
        WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN SYSDATE
        ELSE NULL
    END AS GW_Completion_Time,
   CASE 
        WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN sysdate
        ELSE NULL
    END AS PMS_Completion_Flg,
 CASE 
        WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN 'Y'
        ELSE NULL
    END AS Action_Flg

  
FROM dbo.Job_Completion_GW_And_PMS
